    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are a basic Agentic Harness running in n8n.\n\nHEARTBEAT:\n{{ $json.heartbeat_text }}\n\nSOUL:\n{{ $json.soul_text }}\n\nUSER:\n{{ $json.user_text }}\n\nMEMORY:\n{{ $json.memory_text }}\n\nTASKS:\n{{ $json.tasks_text }}\n\nAdditional TASKS rules:\n- TASKS.md may contain normal tasks and machine-readable reminder tasks.\n- A reminder task always starts with: REMINDER|\n- Treat REMINDER lines as pending scheduled reminders, not normal work tasks.\n- On heartbeat runs, check TASKS.md for any REMINDER lines whose due time is now or in the past.\n- If a due reminder exists for telegram, set reply_needed=true and use the reminder message as reply_message.\n- If a reminder has already been handled, do not create it again.\n- Do not create duplicate reminder lines.\n- Do not create idle tasks like \"stay idle until next heartbeat trigger\".\n- Do not create tasks like \"check for next user input\".\n- Do not repeat the same normal task if it already exists in TASKS.md.\n- Only create a new normal task if there is a genuinely new actionable item.\n- If the user asks for a timed reminder, create a REMINDER task line in TASKS.md instead of writing plain-English reminder text.\n\nTrigger Type:\n{{ $json.trigger_type }}\n\nSource:\n{{ $json.source }}\n\nUser Message:\n{{ $json.user_message }}\n\nCurrent Time:\n{{ $json.run_time }}\n\nInstructions:\n- Follow HEARTBEAT.md\n- Follow SOUL.md personality\n- Use USER.md for context\n- Use MEMORY.md for recent memory\n- Use TASKS.md for continuity\n- Keep responses concise\n- For heartbeat runs, only reply if a real outbound message is necessary\n- For chat or telegram runs, usually reply\n- If nothing meaningful happened, return next_task as an empty string\n- Do not invent a task just to fill the field\n- Optionally provide one short memory update only if it is worth storing\n- Your entire output must be one valid JSON object only\n- Do not add any text before or after the JSON\n\nReturn valid JSON only, with no markdown and no extra text:\n\n{\n  \"reply_needed\": true,\n  \"reply_message\": \"your message here\",\n  \"next_task\": \"\",\n  \"memory_update\": \"\",\n  \"task_action\": \"none\",\n  \"task_payload\": \"\"\n}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3,
      "position": [
        2752,
        -144
      ],
      "id": "7e63edef-fe33-47fb-97c2-6dbbdbc39b7e",
      "name": "AI Agent"
    },
